exercises.name: Barbell Bench Press
exercises.instructions: Lie on flat bench. Lower bar to chest, press up to full extension.

exercises.name: Incline Barbell Bench Press
exercises.instructions: Set bench to 30-45 degrees. Press barbell from upper chest.

exercises.name: Decline Barbell Bench Press
exercises.instructions: Set bench to decline position. Press barbell from lower chest.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Bench Press
exercises.instructions: Press dumbbells from chest level to full extension, maintaining control.

exercises.name: Incline Dumbbell Press
exercises.instructions: On incline bench, press dumbbells up from shoulder level.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Flyes
exercises.instructions: On flat bench, arc dumbbells out and down, then squeeze back together.

exercises.name: Cable Crossover
exercises.instructions: Pull high cables down and across body, squeezing chest at center.

exercises.name: Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Lower body until chest nearly touches floor, push back up.

exercises.name: Dips
exercises.instructions: Lean forward, lower body by bending elbows, push back up.

exercises.name: Pec Deck Machine
exercises.instructions: Bring handles together in front of chest, control release.

exercises.name: Barbell Row
exercises.instructions: Hinge at hips, pull barbell to lower chest, squeeze shoulder blades.

exercises.name: Deadlift
exercises.instructions: Lift barbell from floor by extending hips and knees simultaneously.

exercises.name: Romanian Deadlift
exercises.instructions: Lower barbell with slight knee bend, feel hamstring stretch, return to standing.

exercises.name: Pull-Ups
exercises.instructions: Hang from bar, pull body up until chin over bar.

exercises.name: Chin-Ups
exercises.instructions: Underhand grip, pull body up emphasizing biceps and lats.

exercises.name: Lat Pulldown
exercises.instructions: Pull bar down to upper chest, squeeze shoulder blades together.

exercises.name: Seated Cable Row
exercises.instructions: Pull handle to torso, squeeze back at contraction.

exercises.name: T-Bar Row
exercises.instructions: Pull loaded end of barbell to chest while stabilizing body.

exercises.name: Single-Arm Dumbbell Row
exercises.instructions: Support body on bench, row dumbbell to hip.

exercises.name: Face Pulls
exercises.instructions: Pull rope attachment to face level, externally rotate shoulders.

exercises.name: Overhead Press
exercises.instructions: Press barbell from shoulders to overhead, lock out at top.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Shoulder Press
exercises.instructions: Press dumbbells overhead from shoulder height.

exercises.name: Arnold Press
exercises.instructions: Start with palms facing you, rotate and press overhead.

exercises.name: Lateral Raises
exercises.instructions: Raise dumbbells out to sides until parallel with floor.

exercises.name: Front Raises
exercises.instructions: Raise dumbbells in front of body to shoulder height.

exercises.name: Rear Delt Flyes
exercises.instructions: Bent over, raise dumbbells out to sides focusing on rear delts.

exercises.name: Upright Row
exercises.instructions: Pull barbell up front of body to chin level.

exercises.name: Shrugs
exercises.instructions: Elevate shoulders straight up, squeeze traps at top.

exercises.name: Barbell Curl
exercises.instructions: Curl barbell up to shoulders, keep elbows stationary.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Curl
exercises.instructions: Curl dumbbells alternating or simultaneously to shoulders.

exercises.name: Hammer Curl
exercises.instructions: Curl dumbbells with neutral grip (palms facing each other).

exercises.name: Preacher Curl
exercises.instructions: Curl barbell with arms braced on preacher bench.

exercises.name: Cable Curl
exercises.instructions: Curl cable attachment to shoulders, constant tension.

exercises.name: Concentration Curl
exercises.instructions: Seated, brace elbow on inner thigh, curl dumbbell up.

exercises.name: Close-Grip Bench Press
exercises.instructions: Bench press with hands closer than shoulder width.

exercises.name: Tricep Dips
exercises.instructions: Keep body upright, lower and press focusing on triceps.

exercises.name: Overhead Tricep Extension
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbell overhead, lower behind head, extend up.

exercises.name: Tricep Pushdown
exercises.instructions: Push cable attachment down to full elbow extension.

exercises.name: Skull Crushers
exercises.instructions: Lower barbell to forehead level, extend back up.

exercises.name: Diamond Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Push-ups with hands forming diamond shape under chest.

exercises.name: Barbell Squat
exercises.instructions: Lower body by bending knees and hips, return to standing.

exercises.name: Front Squat
exercises.instructions: Hold bar across front shoulders, perform squat.

exercises.name: Goblet Squat
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbell at chest, perform deep squat.

exercises.name: Bulgarian Split Squat
exercises.instructions: Rear foot elevated, lower front leg into lunge position.

exercises.name: Leg Press
exercises.instructions: Press platform away using legs, control return.

exercises.name: Leg Extension
exercises.instructions: Extend lower legs until knees are straight.

exercises.name: Lunges
exercises.instructions: Step forward into lunge, alternate legs.

exercises.name: Leg Curl
exercises.instructions: Curl legs up toward glutes against resistance.

exercises.name: Nordic Hamstring Curl
exercises.instructions: Kneel, lower body forward with control, hamstrings resist.

exercises.name: Good Mornings
exercises.instructions: Hinge at hips with bar on shoulders, return to standing.

exercises.name: Hip Thrust
exercises.instructions: Shoulders on bench, thrust hips up squeezing glutes.

exercises.name: Glute Bridge

exercises.name: Cable Pull-Through
exercises.instructions: Pull cable between legs by extending hips, squeeze glutes.

exercises.name: Standing Calf Raise
exercises.instructions: Raise up on toes, lower with control.

exercises.name: Seated Calf Raise
exercises.instructions: Seated, push up on toes against resistance.

exercises.name: Calf Raise on Leg Press
exercises.instructions: On leg press, push platform with toes only.

exercises.name: Plank
exercises.instructions: Hold body in straight line on forearms and toes.

exercises.name: Crunches
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, curl shoulders toward hips.

exercises.name: Hanging Leg Raises
exercises.instructions: Hang from bar, raise legs to parallel or higher.

exercises.name: Russian Twists
exercises.instructions: Seated with feet up, rotate torso side to side.

exercises.name: Cable Woodchoppers
exercises.instructions: Pull cable diagonally across body in chopping motion.

exercises.name: Ab Wheel Rollout
exercises.instructions: Roll wheel forward, maintain tight core, return.

exercises.name: Mountain Climbers

exercises.name: Bicycle Crunches
exercises.instructions: Alternate bringing opposite elbow to opposite knee.

exercises.name: Farmer's Walk

exercises.name: Burpees

exercises.name: Kettlebell Swings

exercises.name: Clean and Press

exercises.name: Snatch

exercises.name: Thrusters
exercises.instructions: Front squat directly into overhead press.

exercises.name: Box Jumps
exercises.instructions: Jump explosively onto elevated box, step down.

exercises.name: Battle Ropes

exercises.name: Sled Push

exercises.name: Wall Balls

exercises.name: Plate Pinch

exercises.name: Incline Bench Press (Smith Machine)

exercises.name: Hyperextensions

exercises.name: Incline Dumbbell Curl

exercises.name: Dumbbell Kickback
